  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sewing Sanitary Pads to create Livelihoods Support</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many of us take for granted several things: 1) access to income generating activities to be able to provide for our families 2) female hygiene products available each month 3) even during our menstruation, we can stay in school and 4) the ability to dispose of our sanitary products in a way that doesn&apos;t compromise the health of our environment.  People in rural communities in South Africa do not have this luxury. Our Sewing project - focused on reusable sanitary pads addresses these needs.</narrative>
  </description>
